644
00:39:35,401 --> 00:39:38,469
Vamos, mexam-se!

645
00:39:38,470 --> 00:39:41,106
E... tempo.

646
00:39:41,107 --> 00:39:44,075
3 min 47 seg.
Nada mal.

647
00:39:47,329 --> 00:39:48,643
Herrmann!

648
00:39:49,615 --> 00:39:53,201
