651
00:39:57,506 --> 00:39:59,591
Meu Deus.

652
00:39:59,592 --> 00:40:04,461
Aguenta firme.

653
00:40:20,695 --> 00:40:23,031
Olá.

654
00:40:23,032 --> 00:40:24,682
Que dia, não?

655
00:40:24,683 --> 00:40:26,683
Sim.

656
00:40:28,853 --> 00:40:30,688
